page.title: 19A Tuesday in the Life of Me
page.content: I am{Janicen Mogridge}this is about a Tuesday in the life of me. I wake up at 6.45 and read till my dad calls me to get washed. When I'm washed and dressed I go downstairs and help my dad cook the breakfast. At school when the bell goes we have our assembly. Mrs. Thorpe takes it. She talks about nature. Her assemblies are very enjoyable and interesting.After assembly we go swimming at Milldene. Mrs. Marchant is our swimming teacher. She teaches new strokes. When we get to school we have to wait about 1 hour and then its lunchtime. I have school dinners. After school at 7.15 I go to guides. This ends at 8.45. Its fun at guides. I have just been enrolled as I am ten.
